    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8 with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the M-DCT dual-clutch transmission, offering lightning-fast shifts and rev-matched downshifts. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping rates. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the high-revving internals are protected. Finished in Interlagos Blue over Novillo leather, the car displays minor stone chipping consistent with spirited use but remains mechanically robust with linear power delivery and a visceral induction note. A true driver\u2019s spec featuring the M-Variable differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction.",
      "price": 34500.0,
